vernac_cmds: From ChargeCore.Logics Require Import ILogic ILEmbed.
Definition Fun (A B : Type) := A -> B.
Context T (ord: relation T) {HPre : PreOrder ord}.
Record ILPreFrm := mkILPreFrm { ILPreFrm_pred :> T -> A; ILPreFrm_closed: forall t t': T, ord t t' -> ILPreFrm_pred t |-- ILPreFrm_pred t' }.
Global Instance ILPreFrm_m (P: ILPreFrm): Proper (ord ++> lentails) (ILPreFrm_pred P).
Program Definition ILPreFrm_atom (a : A) := mk (fun t => a) _.
Local Obligation Tactic := repeat match goal with | |- ord _ _ -> _ => intros Hord; try setoid_rewrite Hord; reflexivity | |- _ => intro end.

Global Program Instance ILPre_Ops : ILogicOps ILPreFrm := {| lentails P Q := forall t:T, (ILPreFrm_pred P) t |-- (ILPreFrm_pred Q) t; ltrue := mk (fun t => ltrue) _; lfalse := mk (fun t => lfalse) _; limpl P Q := mk (fun t => Forall t', Forall Ht' : ord t t', (ILPreFrm_pred P) t' -->> (ILPreFrm_pred Q) t') _; land P Q := mk (fun t => (ILPreFrm_pred P) t //\\ (ILPreFrm_pred Q) t) _; lor P Q := mk (fun t => (ILPreFrm_pred P) t \\// (ILPreFrm_pred Q) t) _; lforall A P := mk (fun t => Forall a, (ILPreFrm_pred (P a)) t) _; lexists A P := mk (fun t => Exists a, (ILPreFrm_pred (P a)) t) _ |}.
assert (ord t t'') as Ht'' by (transitivity t'; assumption).
intros P Q R HPQ HQR t.
transitivity ((ILPreFrm_pred Q) t); [apply HPQ | apply HQR].
apply lforallL with x; apply H.
apply lforallR; intro x; apply H.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply H.
apply lexistsR with x; apply H.
apply landR; [eapply H | eapply H0]; assumption.
apply lorL; [eapply H | eapply H0]; assumption.
apply lforallR; intro t'; apply lforallR; intro Hord.
Global Instance ILPreFrm_pred_m {H : PreOrder ord}: Proper (lentails ++> ord ++> lentails) ILPreFrm_pred.
intros P P' HPt t t' Ht.
Global Instance ILPreFrm_pred_equiv_m: Equivalence ord -> Proper (lequiv ==> ord ==> lequiv) ILPreFrm_pred.
intros Hord P P' HPt t t' Ht.
Global Instance ILPreFrm_pred_entails_eq_m: Proper (lentails ++> eq ++> lentails) ILPreFrm_pred.
intros P P' HPt t t' Ht.
Global Instance ILPreFrm_pred_equiv_eq_m: Proper (lequiv ==> eq ==> lequiv) ILPreFrm_pred.
intros P P' HPt t t' Ht.
Program Definition ILPreAtom {HPre : PreOrder ord} (t: T) := mk (fun t' => Exists x : ord t t', ltrue) _.
apply lexistsR; [transitivity t0; assumption | apply ltrueR].
Context T (ord: relation T) {HPre : PreOrder ord}.
Context {HEmbOp : EmbedOp A B} {HEmb : Embed A B}.
Global Program Instance EmbedILPreDropOp : EmbedOp A (ILPreFrm ord B) := { embed := fun a => mkILPreFrm (fun x => embed a) _ }.
Global Instance EmbedILPreDrop : Embed A (ILPreFrm ord B).
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlforall.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlexists.
apply lforallR; intro x; apply lforallR; intro H.
Global Program Instance EmbedILPreOp : EmbedOp (ILPreFrm ord A) (ILPreFrm ord B) := { embed := fun a => mkILPreFrm (fun x => embed ((ILPreFrm_pred a) x)) _ }.
Global Instance EmbedILPre : Embed (ILPreFrm ord A) (ILPreFrm ord B).
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlforall.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlexists.
split; intros t; simpl; do 2 setoid_rewrite <- embedlforall; apply lforallR; intro t'; apply lforallR; intro H; apply lforallL with t'; apply lforallL with H; apply embedImpl.

Global Program Instance ILFun_Ops : ILogicOps ((fun x y => x -> y) T A) := {| lentails P Q := forall t:T, P t |-- Q t; ltrue := fun t => ltrue; lfalse := fun t => lfalse; limpl P Q := fun t => P t -->> Q t; land P Q := fun t => P t //\\ Q t; lor P Q := fun t => P t \\// Q t; lforall A P := fun t => Forall a, P a t; lexists A P := fun t => Exists a, P a t |}.
intros P Q R HPQ HQR t.
apply lforallL with x; apply H.
apply lexistsR with x; apply H.
Definition toProp (P : option A) := match P with | Some P => P | None => lfalse end.

Global Program Instance ILOption_Ops : ILogicOps (option A) := {| lentails P Q := toProp P |-- toProp Q ; ltrue := Some ltrue ; lfalse := Some lfalse ; limpl P Q := Some (toProp P -->> toProp Q) ; land P Q := Some (toProp P //\\ toProp Q) ; lor P Q := Some (toProp P \\// toProp Q) ; lforall A P := Some (Forall a, toProp (P a)) ; lexists A P := Some (Exists a, toProp (P a)) |}.
intros P Q R HPQ HQR.
apply lforallL with x; apply H.
apply lexistsR with x; apply H.
Context {HEmbOp : EmbedOp A B} {HEmb : Embed A B}.
Program Instance EmbedILFunDropOp {T} : EmbedOp A (T -> B) := { embed := fun a t => embed a }.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlforall.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlexists.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedImpl.
Program Instance EmbedILFunOp {T} : EmbedOp (T -> A) (T -> B) := { embed := fun a x => embed (a x) }.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlforall.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedlexists.
split; intros t; simpl; apply embedImpl.
